make a line, right?

41:09.980 --> 41:11.980
Okay. Well, thanks, guys.

41:22.460 --> 41:23.980
How is he?

41:25.020 --> 41:28.860
Did you notice that
Richard has 10 fingers and 10 toes?

41:30.740 --> 41:32.820
I love his little fingernails,

41:33.460 --> 41:34.820
they're like paper.

41:37.100 --> 41:38.180
He looks good.

41:41.460 --> 41:42.740
We won't know for certain

41:42.900 --> 41:45.420
for about 6 months if he's HIV negative...

41:45.900 --> 41:47.260
But it looks good.

41:49.260 --> 41:51.660
Soon you'll be able to take him home, and

41:52.100 --> 41:53.740
get on with your life.

41:55.820 --> 41:57.980
I'm just starting to let myself think about...

41:58.780 --> 42:00.620
stupid things,

42:01.900 --> 42:06.060
like is he gonna love
crossword puzzles like I do?

42:06.220 --> 42:08.820
Is he gonna hate strained peas?

42:10.380 --> 42:13.260
- I know don't, maybe I shouldn't...
- Of course you should.

42:13.940 --> 42:15.820
You should think about the future.

42:17.660 --> 42:19.420
Now Richard has one.

42:22.860 --> 42:25.180
We found a cocktail,
I'm sending it to you.

42:26.140 --> 42:27.260
<i>What am I gonna do with it?</i>

42:27.580 --> 42:29.540
I know you have
connections in South Africa,

42:29.700 --> 42:33.300
you can have the drug reverse-engineered
and shipped to clinics in Mozambique.

42:34.020 --> 42:35.580
<i>No such thing as proper channels?</i>

42:36.420 --> 42:38.540
Come on Jack,
you know that would take too long.

42:38.900 --> 42:41.180
By the time it would get
to Mozambique, more of this strain

42:41.300 --> 42:42.780
could surface and stumble out of control

42:42.860 --> 42:45.020
but if you do it,
you can get it there pronto.

42:46.180 --> 42:49.220
<i>Tell me, Carlos. When am I
getting back my favourite doctor?</i>

42:52.020 --> 42:54.700
You know, I yearn to go back
to Africa, Jack, I really do.

42:54.980 --> 42:57.420
I love the people
and I want to help them,

42:58.380 --> 43:01.860
but I made a bigger impact
on HIV the last few days at NORBAC

43:01.980 --> 43:03.740
than I did 18 months in Africa.

43:04.940 --> 43:06.860
This is where I'm meant to be.

43:07.460 --> 43:08.500
<i>Okay.</i>

43:09.340 --> 43:10.740
Goodbye, my friend.

43:11.620 --> 43:12.540
<i>Bye.</i>

43:13.620 --> 43:15.460
<i>Ruby McGhee. I'm 7 years,</i>

43:15.500 --> 43:17.820
<i>11 months and 12 days old.</i>

43:18.020 --> 43:19.900
<i>- Your birthday's coming up.
- Yup.</i>

43:19.980 --> 43:23.460
<i>- You having a party?
- Two: one for my granny and cousins</i>

43:23.700 --> 43:26.220
<i>and one for all my friends at school.</i>

43:27.380 --> 43:29.860
<i>When I turn 9, I'm getting...</i>

43:30.060 --> 43:31.420
<i>I'm having a sleepover,</i>

43:31.540 --> 43:34.420
<i>and when I turn 16,
I'm getting a Porsche Boxter.</i>

43:35.500 --> 43:38.420
<i>- Sounds you got big plans, Ruby.
- Yup.</i>

44:10.620 --> 44:12.180
Bob, meet Glen.

44:13.380 --> 44:14.500
Hi, Glen.

44:45.860 --> 44:47.580
<i>Next time on ReGenesis:</i>

44:47.660 --> 44:50.020
We have 3 hours before the conference.
That should give us enough time.

44:50.020 --> 44:51.780
- Eat your breakfast.
- Hey! Come on, Bob.

44:59.500 --> 45:01.900
You really think
it's safe to be down here?

45:02.060 --> 45:03.500
What do you want, then?

45:03.700 --> 45:05.500
A couple weeks ago,
she started feeling bad,

45:05.620 --> 45:08.940
and then she started getting
dizzy and she lost her appetite.

45:09.180 --> 45:11.420
She needs to see a fucking doctor, okay?

45:11.580 --> 45:14.780
We're talking about
a cure for juvenile diabetes.

45:14.940 --> 45:16.500
Oh, my God!

45:16.860 --> 45:18.380
Should he deteriorate further,
would you like us

45:18.460 --> 45:20.220
to take measures to sustain his life?

45:20.380 --> 45:22.540
Why do you people keep asking me that?

45:22.780 --> 45:24.940
I'm sorry. You do understand

45:25.060 --> 45:28.180
that what we're doing is not helping Glen,
it's just keeping him alive.

45:28.980 --> 45:30.620
I understand.

45:31.740 --> 45:35.500
We've intercepted messages from hackers
trying to crack NORBAC's website.

45:35.660 --> 45:37.780
If you would rather work
with us than against us,

45:37.820 --> 45:41.020
become a NORBAC field agent
and receive a new mission each week.

45:41.180 --> 45:43.460
Remember, only you know
the whole story.

45:43.620 --> 45:46.420
Become a part
of it at regenesistv.com.

